<inglise> Article 19d </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 19d </eesti>
<inglise> No later than 30 June 1997, the Council shall decide on the provisions proposed by the Commission on catch reporting and on the integrated computerized system for controlling the data referred to in Article 19b. </inglise>
